Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.19,0:25:52.67,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,320)\fad(100,100)}快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.52,0:25:54.09,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,320)\fad(100,100)}陷阱没有解除吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.68,0:25:54.46,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,350)\fad(100,100)}糟糕  我忘记了
