Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.49,0:01:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.59,0:02:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到  无法容忍死掉战线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.15,0:02:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有些唐突  不过你能加入我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说明你已经死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我有点搞不清状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是死后的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不做的话会被消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被消灭掉？  被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要加入的又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「无法容忍死掉战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部队的名称倒是经常会变
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是「死后世界战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过叫死后世界战线的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就等于承认自己已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此砍掉作废  之后就一直变来变去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是叫「无法容忍死掉战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.56,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的是「没感觉还活着战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这句话被别人说过  所以一天之后就换掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你手上的是真枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里的家伙们都是这种反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高你的适应力  去接受这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受现实…  那我要怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟什么战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个就是无法容忍死掉战线的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是尽快把「无法容忍死掉战线」这个名字改掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我想一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不管怎么看都只是一个普通的女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙到底在说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  我能不能到那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！  简直莫名其妙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要怎么想才能得出这种结论
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.31,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死一次看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在这个死不了的世界里常讲的一个笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  笑一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管笑话的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少那边看起来比用枪指着女孩子的家伙更正常一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你说不能用枪的话  那我就不用好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  游离子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人挖脚的事情怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.56,0:04:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在人手不够  就算是再肮脏的手段也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是到那边去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇！  挖脚失败了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.93,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什么啊  那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  刚才有人用枪瞄着你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说你是天使什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是什么天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说啊  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真笨死了  被那个女的给捉弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  连自己是谁都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我还是去一趟医院好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里没有医院的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有人会生病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会生病？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为大家都已经死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是明白了  你也是他们一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想骗我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么  连我的失忆也是你们干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失忆是常有的事情  刚到这里的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果死于非命的话  常常会毁掉脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就证明给我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经死掉了  不会再死…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「handsonic」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还活着  明明那么的痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚是怎么回事  但我不能再留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侮辱游离子  拒不入伙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下  冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  真搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不了的世界的笑话  很好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100次！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:07:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死吧  死吧  死吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再侮辱游离子的话  我还会送你上天的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想杀了我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…  已经不能算是吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这算哪门子的笑话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼得要死却死不了  真够受的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是死后的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不干的话会被消灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  被消灭掉就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就能跟这个世界说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有值得信任的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  去找大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大人们都上哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不去问一下校长好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  那这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死的人是你战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那岂不是我要被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然说的是那个女的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:10.20,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死的人是你战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…  糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实像我会被杀掉似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他呢  没有其他名字了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是不是很霸气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「走马灯战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是马上要死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「敢死队战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是准备好去死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「穷途末路战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经穷途末路了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么「无敌舰队」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次连战线都不是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「玉碎战队」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.42,0:08:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我揍你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「莱特兄弟」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  一定要用战线结尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点不能妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是要站在战场第一线的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能起个好一点的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  那个人已经醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我也让这家伙去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑的时间已经够多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来听听怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:08:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给「无法容忍死掉战线」起的新队名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「随便闹吧战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子  竟然敢违抗游离子胆子不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.43,0:09:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是在说让你们随便闹吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底算什么啊  你们这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我也扯进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我巴不得立即消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想消失？  就算你现在存在于这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经给他解释过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算不做反抗就消失掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算不做反抗就变成水蚤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  水蚤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你以为灵魂只会寄宿在人类体内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定来生会变成藤壶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是寄居蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已无力吐槽为什么全都是海边生物了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一说这毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快从这里滚出去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要顺从天使顺利转世的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成藤壶能被人吃掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不也是种挺幸福的来生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  藤壶能吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有能食用的种类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道唉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  大家别说这些好像要赶他走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可怜的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…刚才说到什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「藤壶战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  由我们藤壶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归原点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「死后世界战线」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好腿法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个战线的本部里还是很安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是因此才逃到这里来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚想进来时还被打飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  来生可能不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是没法证明的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道有人看见过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然不能证明了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是佛教中认为来生不一定就转世成人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…变成藤壶什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然宗教也是人想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你听好了  现在我要说重点了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我们过去所生活的世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的死亡是无差别不可预料的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也无从抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在这个世界却不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要反抗天使就能继续存在  是可以抗争的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是等等  之后又会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目的是消灭天使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并获得这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才来没多久  所以会觉得混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高自己的适应力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去接受这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后战斗吗  和天使…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  和我们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别操之过急  游离…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然中了自己设置的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也像那样飞起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想安全进来是需要暗号的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是「对天使用作战本部」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除这里以外就没有能放心谈话的场所了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出去考虑的话请随便
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么暗号是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「无神无佛无天使」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是由理  是这条战线的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是日向君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.07,0:12:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和看上去一样吊儿郎当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但该认真时偶尔还是会认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么介绍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是松下君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.47,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为柔道五段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就尊称他为松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.78,0:12:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是大山君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有特征就是他的特征
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到战线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come  on  let's  dance
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我可不会跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.50,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和人打招呼就是像这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:07.80,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都叫他TK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道他的真名  迷一样的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的人当伙伴不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是扶眼镜说话显得很有文化的是高松君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.65,0:13:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有他是藤卷君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是藤卷  小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外刚才飞出去的是野田君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在角落总是说「真是肤浅」的是椎名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.47,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在这里的是岩泽同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻部队的头领
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在场的战线成员还有好几十人  他们都潜伏在校园里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来还没问过你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那个…音…音无
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有记忆的那类型吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  总会想起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  不给他制服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是  忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  为什么我的衣服…和你们不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的不同  而是我们的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿的是模范生的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这是我们SSS的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的学园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.75,0:14:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总人数2000以上  全日制的大型学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里说话不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战计划以外的话当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.21,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  那是罐装咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,key咖啡  很好喝的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  他们是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是在忙社团和回家什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样做的话会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:14:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺从天使去上课参加社团的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.14,0:15:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这些人就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思好像他们不是人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:10.50,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是NPC
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NPC？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道吗  Non-Player  Character
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打比方嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是一开始就存在于这个世界的模范
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么他们没有自我意识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和他们对话也只会回答同样的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚来这里  估计分不出他们和我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以正常对话的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不你去爆女孩子的菊花试试
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆菊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不逃走要不就是踢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得还真是不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一说NPC是不会老的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凶暴的天使是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一见面我就被她刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看到了  但那是你自己活该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要天使证明你死不了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她当然会刺你的心脏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对她来说就好像是回答别人办公室的所在而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说天使遵从着这个世界的规则吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是笨拙罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有自我意识的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢  是个迷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无感情无表情基本不说话  就这点来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比普通的NPC有个性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一般来说会像那样轻易去杀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…轻易就动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不像模范生那样进行校内活动的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是口头警告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑的话就会追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会绕到前方阻挡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会动武吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以牙还牙  也就是当我们先行攻击的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像对待我这样直接动手的情况也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外举止别向模范看齐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人因此就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我坚信它存在  虽然还没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有问过天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这个世界构成的问题似乎都是无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  学习会结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  我并没有完全融入他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我最优先考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是平安度过取回记忆前的这段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  音无君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是新手也能用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准对方的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样她就追不了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对女孩子开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤立刻就会恢复的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种问题你亲自体验一下就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是这样过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:17:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答得很好  音无君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你能尽快适应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先参加我们日常的一个小战役吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战名 「龙卷风行动」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次来了个超大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙  龙卷风？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学生的手里把餐券卷走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这个「卷走」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一点也不大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是欺负别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太让我失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就仗着武器和人多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  这是对游离子的侮辱性发言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把刚才那句话收回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们保护濒危藤壶战线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝不会以人数和武力来威胁普通学生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个要灭绝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她不是说要「卷走」的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  正是名副其实的「卷走」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  你属于阻止天使前进的路障班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把作战地点的食堂围起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.26,0:18:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自在指定的地点武装待机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  会给你安排一个轻松的位置的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体的位置等一会儿向高松君和大山君确认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩泽同学  今天也期待你的出色表现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使一旦出现就立刻开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会成为请求支援的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你听到别处有枪声也要立刻赶过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始时刻是1830
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个作战到底要怎么把餐券和平地卷走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是游佐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照明班和音响班均准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌迷们已经察觉到并正聚集过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.41,0:19:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是GDM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱会开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我这边出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说明我这里是现在战线的弱点所在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被看扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  我就开枪给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要对那纤细的身体开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不干掉她  就会被她干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不留情地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  明明打脚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧  已经
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「guard  skill」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「handsonic」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么她没停下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么啊  那是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.60,0:22:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:17.32,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get you reload kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然瞄准了我们最薄弱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是「handsonic」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.96,0:22:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到开阔一点的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边后退一边集中火力攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「guard  skill」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「distortion」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my  god
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说枪太废了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.75,0:23:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拖延时间而已  没想到竟然变成这么激烈的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宴会进入高潮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.94,0:23:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（肉乌冬）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就可以了吗  那快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  肉乌冬  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.84,0:24:17.73,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  super  delicious. Oh  yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗  在这种地方悠闲地吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会来袭击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.80,0:24:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只不过是在吃饭而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的逻辑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.63,0:24:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有这样的领导才能和力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.41,0:24:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以想做什么就做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.67,0:24:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却这样朴素地吃着饭生活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.30,0:24:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人真的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.75,0:24:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有天使
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.59,0:24:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是和她战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.99,0:24:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要正当化吗  把这行为
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.92,0:24:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.27,0:24:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.03,0:24:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.73,0:25:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.95,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}背後はシャッターの壁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:21.58,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}指先は鉄の匂い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.42,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}進め　弾け
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:29.71,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どのみち混むでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:36.12,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:41.70,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}found out　見つける
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:47.09,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}rockを奏でろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:52.65,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}遠くを見据えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.68,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}息継ぎさえできない街の中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.60,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星空が最高の舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:07.39,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}カラスたちカーカーと鳴くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.01,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつも思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.93,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつ寝てるんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:20.23,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　あたしも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:25.82,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}song for　歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:31.30,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}rockを響かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:36.90,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}crowを歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.53,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでこんなところに居る？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.22,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう言う奴もいた気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.99,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}うるさいことだけ言うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:57.61,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}漆黒の羽にさらわれて消えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.45,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全力でもう倒れそうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:29.41,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}指もすり切れて痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.03,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}でもね　演るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:37.04,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今夜もビッグなストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:43.71,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.23,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}found out　見つける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:54.76,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}rockを奏でろ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:00.23,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}luckを歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.91,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでだってここに居るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:05.75,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}通り過ぎていく人の中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:08.57,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}闇に閉ざされたステージで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:11.19,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今希望の詩歌うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.97,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あなただって疲れてるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:16.75,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その背中にも届けたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.48,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}こんな暗闇の中からの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:26.63,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}希望照らす光の歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:32.87,INJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:15.95,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}背后是一道卷帘门
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:21.58,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}指尖有钢铁的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.42,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要客气  弹奏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:29.71,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}反正都要引起一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:36.12,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　从此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:41.70,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}found out　察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:47.09,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}rock 演奏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:52.65,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}紧盯着远方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.68,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在这片刻喘息也没有的城市中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:01.60,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}星空是最棒的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:07.39,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}乌鸦们也哇哇叫个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.01,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我总是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.93,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}难道它们不用睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:20.23,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　我也如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:25.82,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}song for　开始歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:31.30,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}rock 奏响起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:36.90,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}crow 歌唱起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.90,0:21:39.53,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你想一直留到什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.22,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}似乎听见有人这么说道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.99,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}假若只说这些恼人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:57.61,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就快被漆黑的羽翼卷走消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:23.45,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}用尽全力仿佛就要倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.22,0:22:29.41,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手指也如利刃划过般痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:34.03,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但是  依然要演奏下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.03,0:22:37.04,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今晚也是一场激烈的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:43.71,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}find a way　从此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:49.23,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}found out　察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.23,0:22:54.76,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}rock 演奏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:00.23,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}luck 歌唱起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.91,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无论何时都将一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:05.75,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那些经过这里的人群之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.75,0:23:08.57,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在这被黑暗笼罩的舞台之上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:11.19,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如今将高唱希望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.97,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你也一定很累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.97,0:23:16.75,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}希望能成为你的依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:19.48,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一首来自黑暗之中的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:26.63,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一首照亮希望之路的
